{"tid":1308111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我將過去一個月嘅運動令好多人喊過嘅片段擺埋咗一齊","createTime":"2019-07-11T20:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:39:49.000Z","uid":102968,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb6c3ff0f46ddbf8766e4ac8e8944b26bc9eba93","tid":1308111,"uid":102968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:48:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pHZ6S3FAeFY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpHZ6S3FAeFY&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0EPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=911c9483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pHZ6S3FAeFY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢排腦海裏面除咗黑警打人嘅片段之外<br />\n一諗到呢幾段就會不自覺咁喊<br />\n傷心得嚟 我覺得我係因為見到香港人<br />\n可以係危難嘅時候都展現到人性嘅光輝 覺得好可貴 而不自覺咁喊咗出嚟<br />\n香港人加油！ 我哋一定要一齊贏！"},{"pid":"d369cc356139cfea340d61e60ec9bcc97f5d8321","tid":1308111,"uid":102968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:50:29.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"d335ede5c5f519a82bb83e567b406f00920d7981","tid":1308111,"uid":102968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n我要去廁所"},{"pid":"9d282231badea1034b0581f37acad9fc2d3cbce0","tid":1308111,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:21:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9e96146ef5a5e603ad29a93fd0a3624f97f9df2","tid":1308111,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4037cefb0eabd78d6255a9282f590d35610d0c0c","tid":1308111,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2896883b3c37b901974cf66c855d370ef0eab6f","tid":1308111,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor